text:
Nicola Barrett (born 18 February 1993) is a South African water polo player and coach. She competed for the South Africa women's national water polo team in the 2017 World Aquatics Championships and 2019 FINA Women's Water Polo World League.
She played for California State University, Bakersfield's women's water polo team.
